Assignment Title:
`Task Tracker with Calendar Integration and Notifications `

#backend

run command

```
1) npm i
2) setup database
3) nodemon index.js
```

Tech Stack
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Database: MongoDB (Mongoose)
datavalidation zod

API Endpoints

Method Route Description
GET /api/all Get all tasks
GET /api/task/:id Get task by ID
POST /api/new Create new task
PUT /api/update/:id Update task
DELETE /api/delete/:id Delete task
GET /api/complete/:id Mark task completed
GET /api/overdue Get due/overdue tasks
PUT /api/updateDueDate/:id Update due date

feature

prenent dos using rate limiting
data validation used zod libary
